snippet.title: Hes games - C64 full playthrough
snippet.description:
Hes Games is a 1984 sports game released for the Commodore 64 by HESware. It was originally developed by 3-2-1 Software for the C64.

00:00 Intro
01:23 100m sprint
02:24 110m hurdles
03:17 Long jump
07:10 Archery
12:40 Diving
16:18 2-hand snatch
21:19 Clean and jerk
24:54 Credits
